column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
i have problems in my knee what
Has the pain in your knee been constant or have you noticed any aggravating activities? Also, what kind of pain is it? Is it aching, sharp, stabbing, or burning?
Burning stinging pain in your knee could be related to inflammation or an overuse injury. Have you been increasing your activity recently or doing any kind of strenuous physical activity?
